data.description: Looking for a spacious home! Here is the perfect one for you. This home is a move-in ready property and has several attractive features. Here's a summary of the key details and highlights:  Property Details:  4 bedrooms including a Master Room with a tub & separate shower and a walk in closet + a 5th room that can be used as office or guess bedroom. 2.5 bathrooms.  2-car garage.  Partial basement with ample space for family gatherings.  Recent Renovations and Updates:  Renovated brick patio in August 2023, providing a great outdoor space.  New roof replaced in June 2023, ensuring long-term protection.  New carpeting was installed in 3 of the bedrooms in September 2023, adding comfort and aesthetics.  Water heater replacement in November 2022, ensuring reliable hot water supply.  Hardwood floors installed approximately 3 years ago, offering a timeless and elegant look.  The entire house was recently painted last month, giving it a fresh and well-maintained appearance. Garage door was replaced about 4 years ago.
